#. type: multicols*
#: campaigns/inferno_devilish_plan.tex:121
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\textbf{1$^{st}$ Round:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item Read: ``Our underlings have done well. They have managed to raise a volcano\n"
"    and erect a fort in a sparsely populated forest just outside of Erathia's border.\n"
"    While the Dungeon Overlords make their way underground toward the Erathian capitol,\n"
"    you must strike at their allies, the elves of AvLee.''\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: campaigns/inferno_devilish_plan.tex:129
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\textbf{2$^{nd}$ Round:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item Read: ``The Gold Dragon Queen is a powerful ally of AvLee.\n"
"    You must find her lair and see to her demise, as this will greatly weaken\n"
"    the elves and make them less of a threat to our plans to destroy Erathia.\n"
"    Go now, and make us proud!''\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: campaigns/inferno_devilish_plan.tex:135
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\textbf{9$^{th}$ Round:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item The Few Elves of Ivor's Army are Reinforced to a Pack of Elves.\n"
"    Ivor's Army also gains an Ammo Cart.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: campaigns/inferno_devilish_plan.tex:140
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\textbf{10$^{th}$ Round:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item The Rampart Faction Town that Ivor's Army resides in gains an Arrow Tower.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: campaigns/inferno_devilish_plan.tex:145
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\textbf{13$^{th}$ Round:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item At the end of the round, if both the Enemy Hero and the Gold Dragon Armies are not defeated, all is lost - you lose!\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: campaigns/inferno_devilish_plan.tex:150
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\textbf{When you complete the scenario:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item Read: ``Congratulations! You have completed your quest to kill the fearsome beast, and can claim victory!'\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: campaigns/inferno_devilish_plan.tex:153
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{\\MakeUppercase{Additional rules}}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: campaigns/inferno_devilish_plan.tex:155
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"During this ``Inferno'' campaign scenario, the following rules apply:\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols*
#: campaigns/inferno_devilish_plan.tex:164
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item Your Hero does not gain Experience past Level 5.\n"
"    \\item The Enemy Hero does not move and only waits in their Town. They start with Walls and a Gate on their side of the Combat Board.\n"
"    \\item The N7 Map tile cannot be entered until Ivor is defeated.\n"
"    \\item At the Dragon Utopia location, your Hero fights the Gold Dragons Army.\n"
"    \\item The ``Castle Gate'' cannot be built.\n"
"    \\item If your Hero visits an Obelisk, you may Search (2) the Ability deck, the Artifact deck, or the Spell deck.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

